{"seg_id": "seg_0001", "text": "各位专家，下面，我开始我的教学展示。", "start": 0.386, "end": 3.787, "duration": 3.401, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0001.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0001.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0002", "text": "同学们，你听说过运动员全红婵吗？", "start": 3.787, "end": 12.449, "duration": 8.662, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0002.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0002.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0003", "text": "哦，你看过她在东京奥运赛场上的比赛视频吗？", "start": 12.449, "end": 17.571, "duration": 5.122, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0003.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0003.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0004", "text": "你还听说过她成长的一些小故事吗？", "start": 17.571, "end": 23.312, "duration": 5.741, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0004.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0004.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0005", "text": "这位世界跳水双冠王，在 2023 年世界跳水 10 米台的决赛赛场上。", "start": 23.312, "end": 30.114, "duration": 6.802, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0005.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0005.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0006", "text": "再一次惊艳一跳，震撼全场。她用实力征服了全场。现场五位裁判中有三位为她打出了满分。", "start": 30.91, "end": 41.457, "duration": 10.547, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0006.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0006.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0007", "text": "下面，我们一起来欣赏一下她优美的跳姿。全红婵奋力一跳，为国争光。", "start": 41.457, "end": 56.908, "duration": 15.451, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0007.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0007.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0008", "text": "她如此高水平的实力背后，", "start": 56.908, "end": 59.03, "duration": 2.122, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0008.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0008.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0009", "text": "既源于他自己勤奋刻苦的努力，也少不了教练组成员对他跳水运动变化过程图像的精细刻画与精细指导。", "start": 59.806, "end": 71.172, "duration": 11.366, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0009.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0009.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0010", "text": "那么，今天我们也来研究一下如何精细刻画图像的变化趋势。", "start": 71.172, "end": 81.278, "duration": 10.106, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0010.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0010.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0011", "text": "从左至右，图像有什么变化趋势呢？", "start": 81.278, "end": 85.02, "duration": 3.742, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0011.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0011.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0012", "text": "好，你来说说看。", "start": 85.02, "end": 88.301, "duration": 3.281, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0012.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0012.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0013", "text": "先上升。", "start": 88.301, "end": 89.182, "duration": 0.881, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0013.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0013.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0014", "text": "再下降。", "start": 90.194, "end": 94.176, "duration": 3.982, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0014.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0014.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0015", "text": "那么我们该如何用精确的数学语言来表达先上升再下降呢？", "start": 94.176, "end": 101.038, "duration": 6.862, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0015.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0015.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0016", "text": "这就是我们今天要研究的课题：单调性与最大最小值。", "start": 101.038, "end": 119.266, "duration": 18.228, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0016.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0016.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0017", "text": "第一课时，为了方便同学们理解，我们以同学们熟悉的 f(x) 等于 x 平方为例来进行探究。", "start": 124.438, "end": 137.604, "duration": 13.166, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0017.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0017.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0018", "text": "首先，画出函数 f(x) 等于 x 平方的图像，并描述图像的变化趋势。", "start": 137.604, "end": 145.767, "duration": 8.163, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0018.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0018.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0019", "text": "把你的过程通过教学平板投屏，我们一起来研究一下。", "start": 145.767, "end": 151.65, "duration": 5.883, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0019.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0019.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0020", "text": "这位同学他画出的过程是这样，跟你画的一致吗？一致。", "start": 154.07, "end": 161.272, "duration": 7.202, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0020.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0020.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0021", "text": "那么，请你描述一下图像的变化趋势。", "start": 161.272, "end": 164.613, "duration": 3.341, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0021.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0021.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0022", "text": "你认为图像先下降再上升？", "start": 164.613, "end": 170.935, "duration": 6.322, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0022.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0022.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0023", "text": "那何时下降，何时上升呢？", "start": 170.935, "end": 175.976, "duration": 5.041, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0023.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0023.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0024", "text": "观察发现，y 轴左侧是下降的，y 轴右侧是上升的。", "start": 175.976, "end": 182.278, "duration": 6.302, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0024.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0024.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0025", "text": "那我们提炼一下刚才这位同学的回答，也就是 y 轴左侧部分从左到右是下降的，y 轴右侧部分从左到右是上升的。", "start": 183.702, "end": 197.086, "duration": 13.384, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0025.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0025.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0026", "text": "这样我们就从这个图形语言中提炼出了它的图形特征。", "start": 197.086, "end": 203.427, "duration": 6.341, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0026.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0026.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0027", "text": "那么接下来，我们能否用数学的语言翻译一下这个图形特征呢？", "start": 203.427, "end": 210.129, "duration": 6.702, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0027.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0027.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0028", "text": "好，你来试试看哦。", "start": 210.129, "end": 212.83, "duration": 2.701, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0028.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0028.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0029", "text": "初中我们学习过下降用变量语言它的描述是Y随X增大而减小上升用变量语言描述是Y随X增大而增大你的知识学得还是很扎实的那么外轴左侧能否用变量语言来翻译一下呢可以用集合", "start": 213.386, "end": 241.79, "duration": 28.404, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0029.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0029.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0030", "text": "负无穷到 0，这是我们第一章所学的内容。", "start": 243.522, "end": 248.305, "duration": 4.783, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0030.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0030.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0031", "text": "那么轴右侧呢？你认为可以用 0 到正无穷。", "start": 248.305, "end": 254.41, "duration": 6.105, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0031.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0031.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0032", "text": "那么如此一来，我们整理一下就得到了文字语言形式的变化趋势。", "start": 254.41, "end": 261.494, "duration": 7.084, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0032.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0032.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0033", "text": "那也就是在负无穷到 0 上，Y 随 X 增大而减小；在 0 到正无穷上，Y 随 X 增大而增大。", "start": 261.494, "end": 272.202, "duration": 10.708, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0033.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0033.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0034", "text": "那么现在我们需要将这样的文字语言翻译成符号语言", "start": 273.942, "end": 280.556, "duration": 6.614, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0034.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0034.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0035", "text": "那怎么翻译呢", "start": 280.556, "end": 282.72, "duration": 2.164, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0035.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0035.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
{"seg_id": "seg_0036", "text": "请同学们试试", "start": 282.72, "end": 283.462, "duration": 0.742, "clip_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/clips/seg_0036.mp4", "audio_path": "dataset/math/T01/MATH_T01_L01/raw/audio/seg_0036.wav", "subject": "math", "teacher_id": "T01", "lesson_id": "MATH_T01_L01"}
